nodes.text: The Jedi Knight Morningfire led the clone trooper Vornskr Company in a rescue on the planet O'reen in the Unknown Regions after the native species, the O'reenians, took the crew of a Galactic Republic military exploration ship as slaves; the starship had been combing the Unknown Regions for signs of Separatist supply planets when it had stumbled upon O'reen. In the fray, the ruler, or Magnus, of O'reen was killed. The following Magnus vowed to return O'reen to isolationism as a result.
